data.name: About_Content
data.value: Jvedio is a local video management software, which supports scanning local videos and importing software, establishing video library, extracting unique video identification code, automatically classifying videos, adding labels to manage videos, using artificial intelligence to identify actors, supporting translation information, and capturing video pictures based on FFmpeg. It is a smooth and beautiful application software on Window desktop
